### Register a device
POST http://localhost:8080/api/devices
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Workstation-01",
  "ipAddress": "192.168.1.10"
}

### Get all devices
GET http://localhost:8080/api/devices

### Get devices filtered by status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/devices?status=ONLINE

### Get one device (replace 1 with actual ID from create response)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/devices/7

### Update a device
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/devices/3
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "OFFLINE"
}

### Get device status summary with rankings
GET http://localhost:8080/api/devices/summary

### Check health of one device
POST http://localhost:8080/api/devices/1/health-check

### Check health of all devices
POST http://localhost:8080/api/devices/health-check

### Delete a device
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/devices/1

### Check cache stats
GET http://localhost:8080/api/devices/cache/stats

### Get queue stats
GET http://localhost:8080/api/devices/queue/stats
